               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Maṣḥafa gǝnzat “Book of the Funeral Ritual” (fols. 3ra-89ra)&#xD; -
                     Discourse of St Athanasius on death (fols. 3ra-11vb)&#xD; - Maṣḥaf za-wäḍʾat
                     ʾǝm-ʾIyarusalem “Book that Came from Jerusalem” (fols. 11vb-17ra)&#xD; - Homily
                     by St Jacob of Serug for the funeral of priests and deacons (fols.
                     33vb-37va)&#xD; - Prayer of archbishop ʾabbā Sawiros (fols. 56vb-58vb)&#xD; -
                     Homily by ʾabbā Salāmā, Metropolitan of Ethiopia (fols. 65vb-68va)&#xD; II)
                     Ṣalota śǝryätä ḫaṭiʾat “Prayer of Absolution of Sins” (fols. 89ra-93va), (cp.
                     EMML 427(9)).&#xD; &#xD; Additiones 1-3.</summary>
